The Department of Computer Science at the University of Oslo, in the Group
of ``Precise Modelling and Analysis'' has open positions both at Ph.D level
and at Post-Doc level in areas that could be of interest of readers of this
email list. 

----------------------------------------------------------------------
   2-3 PhD-positions  

and 

